# Copy to .env.local and fill in from Supabase Dashboard → Connect
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=sb_publishable_...

# Supabase Dashboard → Authentication → URL Configuration (required for email links):
# Site URL:              http://localhost:3000
# Redirect URLs:         http://localhost:3000/**
#
# If confirmation emails do not arrive:
# 1. Check spam/junk folder
# 2. Supabase Dashboard → Authentication → Logs (look for email send errors)
# 3. Free tier limits built-in email to ~4/hour — wait or add custom SMTP under Project Settings → Auth → SMTP
# 4. For local dev only: Authentication → Providers → Email → disable "Confirm email"
